task.summary: Restructured the test sources directory. Added Thesaurus class (not used yet) Changed the way object positioning works such that the first attempt to place an object is a better and more consistent guess.
Implemented relative position constraints other than "above". Added PhraseMatcher functionality.
Added AnyModel. Added JSON serialization if Knowledge. Fixed a bug where composite objects required an object with a determinant. SentencePart has a toString() method. Made Models visiteable.
Partially implemented data-driven interpreter. Resolved compilation errors for now.
Added support for simple Knowledge lookup with dd-interpreter.
Converted art of the project to Kotlin
